<subSubSection id="1D4EE6CF17B4EF11BD9D9EACFC438F5F" pageId="0" pageNumber="81832" type="notes">
<paragraph id="466E4D02E10B899FAE2F383BFD2C0B28" pageId="0" pageNumber="81832">Notes</paragraph>
<paragraph id="86157D63E532A76F08296639BF548340" pageId="0" pageNumber="81832">No additional beetles have been collected after the first discovery, though we launched numerous flight intercept traps every year at the same spot.</paragraph>
